-COMPILATION:

	* Depends
  		libcppunit version >= 1.10.2  https://sourceforge.net/projects/cppunit/
  		scons version >= 0.96.1       http://www.scons.org/
			-on windows add the scons path to the PATH

	To know the compilation option type in the hkl root directory
	scons -h

	then for exemple on windows
		scons cppunit_inc_path="C:\cppunit-1.10.2\include" cppunit_lib_path="C:\cppunit-1.10.2\lib"
	
	on linux usualy just type
		scons

Bugs email to: Picca Frédéric-Emmanuel <picca@synchrotron-soleil.fr>
